{"tid":383108,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全國人大通過《國歌法》 下月1日生效","createTime":"2017-09-01T08:37:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-01T11:03:52.000Z","uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7e45cfe19ae2e3fb3f55c98a8a6c9b8408de7e69","tid":383108,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T08:37:40.000Z","msg":"【唔好亂唱】<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n近日備受爭議，全國人大常委會建議在10月會議上，提請列入《基本法》附件三的《國歌法》，今日在全國人大常委會通過，規定於今年10月1日起正式實施，新法明確「侮辱國歌」的法律責任，可追究刑事責任，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">同時提出要在中小學應將國歌作為愛國主義教育的重要內容，鼓勵唱國歌</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n香港行政長官林鄭月娥日已經指出，在全國人大常委會通過國歌法草案後，特區政府便會展開工作，研究本地立法，她又稱《國歌法》確保國歌受到尊重，理所當然，且不屬於香港自治範圍之內，社會無需反應過敏。<br />\n有分析指，內地通過國歌法，主要是針對香港，不少香港的示威、體育場合上都會「噓國歌」，但一直沒法被處罰，早已令內地官民不滿。<br />\n<br />\n新華社"},{"pid":"6ff22a479cff4eb94209ed2488a5afe3e73595c6","tid":383108,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T09:50:13.000Z","msg":"屌"},{"pid":"c9b5b021bfbc95818f8ac18090824eea127507f8","tid":383108,"uid":85163,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T09:54:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a12dad92e2d075aad50001d395f284fb1e16563c","tid":383108,"uid":82929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T10:05:35.000Z","msg":"我地要記念填詞人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每次唱國歌都舉佢遺照出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59a4a983ad493348f0fe493df1b26326494d8e10","tid":383108,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T10:41:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早就應該啦，全世界都尊重國歌，得香港班垃圾搞事</blockquote><br />\n5 sin"},{"pid":"12ec9f0338ac762c5b965d9490ca054eee695e79